  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink285-kilavi">oruvaḻit taṇantu vanta talaimakaṟkut tōḻi kūṟiyatu. </p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> What the confidante told the hero who had come, having departed on a temporary absence.</p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink285">
<l>piṉṉiruṅ kūnta ṉaṉṉutaṟ kuṟamakaṇ</l>
<l>meṉṟiṉai nuvaṇai yuṇṭu taṭṭaiyi</l>
<l>ṉaivaṉac ciṟukiḷi kaṭiyu nāṭa</l>
<l>vīṅkuvaḷai nekiḻap pirital</l>
<l>yāṅkuval lunaiyō vīṅkivaṭ ṭuṟantē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>O man from the land</l>
        <l>where the hill-daughter,</l>
        <l>with braided dark tresses and a good forehead,</l>
        <l>having eaten tender millet flour,</l>
        <l>chases the small parakeets</l>
        <l>from the mountain paddy</l>
        <l>with her taṭṭai—</l>
        <l rend="space">how are you able to part,</l>
        <l>abandoning her here,</l>
        <l>so that her tight bangles</l>
        <l>grow loose?</l>
        
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
